longBusinessSummary: Image Protect, Inc., a media company, focuses on microcap news, information, and disclosures. It produces, distributes, contracts, and publishes various content assets for microcap companies and investors, including CEO/exec interviews, press releases, disclosure statements, and video news under the Mcap MediaWire name. The company also engages in the crypto, blockchain, and streaming digital assets business. Image Protect, Inc. was incorporated in 1997 and is based in New York, New York.
